casebody.data:
Christopher W. FILLMORE, petitioner,
v.
INDIANA BELL TELEPHONE COMPANY, INC. No. 18-6792. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 7, 2019.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until January 28, 2019, within which *862to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
